se.js.jesdob
Interface IDob

All Known Implementing Classes:
Dob
public interface IDob

A IDob is a dynamic object, containing various kinds of data. It is possible to add attributes to a dob, and to assign values to these attributes. It is possible to read back the values for a specific attrbitutes. IDobs can be exported to text as json-format, xml-format or dob-format. They can then be saved to files and read as dynamic objects when they are needed.
